Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmalayalam%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fdrishyam-3-box-office-collections-day-4-mohanlal-starrer-sees-modest-sunday-growth-worldwide-total-reaches-rs-141-34-cr%2Farticleshow%2F131298797.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131298797.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMohanlal's%20'Drishyam%203'%20continues%20its%20strong%20box%20office%20performance%2C%20crossing%20Rs%2063%20crore%20gross%20in%20India%20by%20Day%204.%20The%20mystery%20thriller%20saw%20a%20slight%20increase%20on%20Sunday%2C%20with%20the%20Malayalam%20version%20leading%20collections.%20Overseas%20markets%20also%20contributed%20significantly%2C%20pushing%20the%20worldwide%20gross%20to%20an%20impressive%20Rs%20141.34%20crore%20in%20just%20four%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20product%20manager%20who%20used%20Claude%20to%20build%20a%20postcard%20business%20in%204%20hours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221619%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Priscilla%20Tina.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a96c194eb4c909fb2d5da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221214%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPriscilla%20Tina%20used%20Claude%20to%20build%20a%20postcard%20app%20in%20about%20four%20hours.%3Cp%3EPriscilla%20Tina%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPriscilla%20Tina%2C%20a%20product%20manager%2C%20loved%20sending%20postcards%20to%20her%20friends%20while%20traveling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20delivering%20them%20was%20a%20hassle%2C%20so%20she%20created%20an%20app%20with%20Claude%20that%20sends%20postcards%20for%20users.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20it's%20made%20her%20a%20bit%20of%20cash%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Priscilla%20Tina%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20product%20manager%20based%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20tech%20product%20manager%20in%20San%20Francisco%20by%20day%3Cs%3E%2C%3C%2Fs%3E%20and%20a%20content%20creator%20by%20night.%20I%20make%20videos%20to%20inspire%20people%20to%20rediscover%20their%20creativity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20doing%20creative%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-side-hustle-creativity-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eside%20hustles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20experiments%20my%20whole%20life%2C%20and%20I'm%20a%20lover%20of%20all%20things%20analog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20November%2C%20I%20sat%20down%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoders-keep-laptops-open-in-public-ai-agent-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilt%20an%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Claude%20Code%20that%20sends%20postcards%20without%20dealing%20with%20stamps%20or%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a93e13d2-dadb-4436-8e3a-9e5413003d6b%5C%22%3EAnalog%20is%20back%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20including%20myself%2C%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20technology.%20But%20I%20also%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-artists-snail-mail-clubs-analogue-stable-paycheck-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eanalog%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20my%20life%20when%20I%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECut%20to%20now%2C%20I've%20started%20living%20on%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20brainrotting%2C%20looking%20at%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanager-sees-more-ai-slop-changing-feedback-approach-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20slop%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We're%20realizing%20that%20spending%20all%20our%20time%20on%20our%20phones%20isn't%20very%20meaningful.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20also%20finding%20out%20that%20you%20can%20connect%20a%20lot%20better%20when%20socializing%20in%20person%2C%20and%20that%20there%20is%20value%20in%20going%20back%20to%20the%20old%20joys%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20bridge%20the%20divide%20between%20the%20digital%20and%20the%20physical%20world%20and%20help%20connect%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20sending%20postcards%20with%20my%20friends%20for%20years%3B%20it's%20a%20really%20fun%20way%20to%20stay%20in%20touch%20while%20traveling.%20I%20also%20started%20to%20realize%20that%20I%20had%20purchased%20so%20many%20postcards.%20I%20had%20a%20huge%20stack%2C%20and%20it%20was%20super%20inconvenient%20to%20write%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20you%20have%20to%20buy%20stamps%20at%20the%20post%20office%20and%20walk%20to%20one%20of%20those%20mailboxes%20to%20mail%20them.%20I%20wondered%20if%20there's%20an%20easier%20way%20to%20do%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222137a262-6e44-49be-a685-81b9e34b254b%5C%22%3EUsing%20Claude%20to%20build%20an%20app%20in%20four%20hours%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tina's%20Postcard%20Press%20app.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a981eabc4e9d88574ae88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETina%20built%20Postcard%20Press%20with%20Claude%20Code%20before%20a%20product%20conference%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3Cp%3EPriscilla%20Tina%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20signed%20up%20for%20ProductCon%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20a%20prototype%20of%20an%20app%20I%20could%20showcase%20at%20the%20event.%20So%20I%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20for%20Postcard%20Press%2C%20an%20app%20that%20lets%20users%20upload%20pictures%20and%20type%20messages%2C%20which%20connects%20to%20a%20service%20called%20Postgrid%20that%20handles%20printing%20and%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20before%2C%20I%20built%20the%20bare%20bones%20of%20the%20app%20in%20four%20hours%20and%20got%20it%20working%20on%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20shared%20it%20with%20other%20product%20managers%20at%20the%20conference%2C%20they%20asked%20me%20when%20it%20was%20ready%20to%20go%2C%20saying%20they%20wanted%20to%20send%20their%20friends%20postcards%20for%20Christmas.%20That%20gave%20me%20intel%20that%20people%20were%20excited%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20the%20waters%20on%20social%20media%20too%2C%20posting%20a%20video%20about%20it%20that%20got%2020%2C000%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20there%20was%20interest%20in%20it%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20challenge%20myself%20to%20finish%20the%20app%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20Over%20the%20next%20two%20months%20before%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20I%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20monetize%20it%2C%20integrate%20payment%20processing%2C%20and%20launch%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20launched%20it%20in%20December%2C%20more%20than%20100%20postcards%20have%20been%20sent%20through%20Postcard%20Press%2C%20each%20costing%20about%20%242.%20Postgrid's%20services%20cost%20%240.82%2C%20and%20Stripe%20charges%20%240.30%20per%20card%2C%20so%20I'm%20honestly%20not%20making%20much%20profit%20per%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20I%20could%20move%20to%20a%20subscription%20model%20if%20revenue%20were%20the%20goal%2C%20but%20it's%20really%20not%20why%20I%20built%20this%20app%20to%20begin%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2262b6c268-db36-4ce5-a3a5-6fd681a10d54%5C%22%3ESome%20tech%20hiccups%20along%20the%20way%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20an%20engineering%20background%2C%20but%20not%20necessarily%20coding%2C%20so%20I%20needed%20some%20help%20from%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-unlikely-crowd-retirees-children-teens-non-technical-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechie%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20launched%20the%20app%2C%20I%20shared%20it%20with%20some%20of%20my%20friends%2C%20and%20they%20sat%20down%20with%20their%20laptops%20to%20try%20to%20hack%20the%20website.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20friends%20found%20a%20security%20error%20that%20let%20him%20send%2010%20postcards%20without%20paying%20me%20anything%2C%20and%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20fix%20this%20before%20you%20launch%20it%20publicly.%26quot%3B%20The%20experience%20helped%20me%20shore%20up%20the%20app's%20security%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPayments%20were%20also%20a%20big%20hurdle%20for%20me%2C%20because%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20set%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstripe-forward-deployed-ai-accelerator-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStripe%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E%20system%20or%20how%20much%20it%20would%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20friends%20challenged%20me.%20One%20of%20them%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20can%20integrate%20Stripe%20to%20do%20payments%20and%20credit%20card%20payments%20in%2030%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20another%20bet%20against%20it.%20So%20I%20sat%20down%20and%20got%20it%20working%20in%2030%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENormally%2C%20I%20would've%20needed%20a%20developer%20to%20do%20that%2C%20but%20I%20just%20asked%20Claude%20to%20read%20through%20all%20of%20Stripe's%20API%20documentation%2C%20and%20it%20was%20able%20to%20integrate%20a%20payment%20step%20in%20the%20checkout%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220519167c-817c-4e53-9028-7bfe673c0b19%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20of%20many%20analog%20apps%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Priscilla%20Tina%20with%20her%20Postcard%20Press%20app.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a986d94eb4c909fb2d5de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETina%20said%20she's%20already%20working%20on%20other%20analog%20apps.%3Cp%3EPriscilla%20Tina%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C