calUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20lived%20abroad%20for%208%20years%2C%20and%20now%20too%20many%20places%20feel%20like%20home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221901%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20posing%20with%20the%20National%20Congress%20building%20in%20Brasilia%2C%20Brazil%2C%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0c13aeabc4e9d88574b4cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221426%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmanda%20Molenaar%20spent%20most%20of%20her%2020s%20and%2030s%20living%20abroad%3B%20now%20she%20finds%20it%20hard%20to%20answer%20where%20home%20is.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Amanda%20Molenaar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20nearly%20two%20decades%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-abroad-far-away-from-family-moved-back-taiwan-canada-2025-4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eliving%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Amanda%20Molenaar%20no%20longer%20feels%20rooted%20in%20just%20one%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20also%20made%20relationships%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging%2C%20and%20decision-making%20about%20the%20future%20difficult.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%2038%2C%20after%20time%20back%20home%2C%20she%20plans%20to%20move%20abroad%20again%20to%20find%20a%20life%20that%20better%20matches%20her%20ambition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20my%20formative%2020s%20and%2030s%20abroad%2C%20I%20lost%20my%20sense%20of%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%2019%20when%20I%20took%20a%20break%20from%20my%20studies%20and%20spent%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20in%20South%20America%2C%20which%20kick-started%20my%20love%20for%20the%20continent%20and%20for%20living%20in%20a%20different%20culture.%20Since%20then%2C%20I've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsold-everything-moved-argentina-2-sons-been-worth-it-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elived%20in%20Buenos%20Aires%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20London%2C%20Brasilia%2C%20and%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro%2C%20partly%20as%20a%20diplomat%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lifestyle%20that%20suited%20me%20perfectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lived%20in%20all%20these%20places%20for%20relatively%20short%20periods%2C%20between%206%20months%20and%203%20years%2C%20and%20also%20often%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20where%20I'm%20from%2C%20in%20between.%20That%20meant%20a%20lot%20of%20change%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20certain%20permanent%20level%20of%20uprootedness%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20years%20that%20shaped%20me%20as%20an%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20my%20friends%20from%20back%20home%20stayed%20close%20to%20where%20they%20grew%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22412b2beb-6c06-442f-b7e9-67dff017e5c0%5C%22%3EMultiple%20countries%20started%20to%20shape%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20landed%20my%20first%20office%20job%20after%20finishing%20my%20master's%20degree%20in%20London.%20So%20my%20introduction%20to%20the%20corporate%20world%20came%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-in-italy-and-us-most-shocking-cultural-differences-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecultural%20differences%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%20I%20experienced%20office%20politics%20through%20the%20British%20lens%20and%20navigated%20filing%20my%20taxes%20in%20a%20different%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20after%20being%20hired%20by%20the%20Dutch%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20in%20a%20completely%20new%20setting%20as%20a%20diplomat%20in%20Brazil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20building%20a%20life%20in%20another%20language%2C%20creating%20a%20routine%20in%20a%20new%20environment%2C%20and%20navigating%20systems%20that%20worked%20differently%20from%20what%20I%20was%20used%20to%2C%20both%20personally%20and%20professionally.%20I%20remember%20representing%20my%20country%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20Portuguese%20%E2%80%94%20a%20moment%20that%20highlighted%20that%20another%20world%20had%20become%20my%20new%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20many%20other%20defining%20experiences%20that%20happened%20abroad%3A%20burnout%2C%20professional%20growth%2C%20deepening%20friendships%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgave-up-life-abroad-to-follow-partner-split-bad-idea-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efalling%20in%20love%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20living%20through%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%2C%20the%20death%20of%20a%20friend%2C%20and%20navigating%20break-ups.%20As%20I%20continued%20to%20reinvent%20myself%2C%20the%20places%20around%20me%20became%20part%20of%20who%20I%20was%20becoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20soaked%20up%20the%20input%20I%20was%20given.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisiting-every-country-new-life-perspective-move-to-portugal-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEach%20country%20I%20lived%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20helped%20shape%20the%20person%20I%20am%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22534c54be-30f2-4fdd-bcd7-b1f8497345be%5C%22%3EHome%20stopped%20being%20one%20place%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20at%2038%2C%20I%20know%20%26quot%3Bhome%26quot%3B%20isn't%20just%20one%20place%20anymore.%20Of%20course%2C%20I%20miss%20people%20and%20things%20from%20home%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-abroad-expat-singapore-opportunity-far-from-home-guilt-aging-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20live%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20my%20friends%2C%20my%20family%2C%20efficiency%2C%20good%20cheese%2C%20all%20four%20seasons.%20But%20honestly%2C%20I%20miss%20other%20places%20just%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20is%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20London's%20atmosphere.%20The%20nature%20of%20Brasilia.%20The%20streets%20of%20Buenos%20Aires.%20And%20much%20more.%20Home%20is%20all%20the%20places%20that%20shaped%20me%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20feel%20incredibly%20rich%20to%20have%20had%20these%20experiences%2C%20it%20also%20makes%20life%20feel%20more%20complex.%20With%20friends%20around%20the%20world%2C%20my%20heart%20is%20scattered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221564%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holding%20a%20coconut%20on%20the%20beach%20in%20Brazil.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0d707c7684ba33f7380981%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221173%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMolenaar%20has%20lived%20in%20Buenos%20Aires%2C%20London%2C%20Brasilia%2C%20and%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Amanda%20Molenaar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20realized%20my%20question%20is%20not%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20do%20I%20belong%3F%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20rather%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20I%20choose%20between%20lives%20that%20all%20feel%20like%20mine%3F%26quot%3B%20It's%20a%20question%20I've%20heard%20often%20from%20others.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-coach-for-ultrawealthy-children-facing-three-issues-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20as%20a%20life%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20expats%20for%20the%20last%204%20years.%20The%20challenge%20for%20many%20isn't%20actually%20missing%20home%3B%20instead%2C%20it's%20learning%20how%20to%20navigate%20a%20life%20that%20no%20longer%20fits%20into%20one%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-bros-treat-dating-like-a-startup-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edating%20more%20complex%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20willing%20to%20settle%20down%20in%20one%20location%20for%20the%20right%20man%2C%20but%20I%20often%20question%20whether%20we%20could%20fully%20relate%20to%20each%20other%20because%20of%20our%20different%20experiences.%20It%20hasn't%20been%20easy%20finding%20someone%20who%20sees%20life%20through%20the%20same%20lens%20and%20feels%20equally%20excited%20about%20exchanging%20the%20comfort%20of%20the%20known%20for%20new%20opportunities%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20I'm%20now%20in%20that%20kind%20of%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22950f01ce-c134-40c5-a19d-67d69c0fefbb%5C%22%3EI%20learned%20to%20become%20my%20own%20anchor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20spent%20most%20of%20the%20past%20six%20years%20back%20home.%20It%20has%20been%20good%20to%20grow%20more%20roots%20in%20one%20place%20and%20be%20back%20when%20I%20unexpectedly%20lost%20both%20of%20my%20parents%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20realized%20this%20chapter%20has%20come%20to%20an%20end%20and%20that%20I%20want%20an%20environment%20that%20better%20matches%20my%20ambition%20and%20personality.%20In%20a%20few%20months%2C%20I'm%20moving%20to%20Mexico%20City.%20I'm%20very%20excited%20about%20making%20a%20new%20context%20my%20own%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20own%20journey%20has%20taught%20me%20that%20staying%20steady%20in%20a%20global%20life%20is%20hard.%20It's%20easy%20to%20want%20to%20move%20when%20the%20novelty%20wears%20off%2C%20and%20hard%20to%20choose%20when%20everything%20feels%20like%20an%20option.%20I've%20learned%20that%20I%20have%20to%20be%20my%20own%20anchor%20in%20a%20life%20with%20different%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-abroad-feel-like-home-diplomat-life-coach-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779666301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0c13edecd7cc1332bb0f7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-abroad-feel-like-home-diplomat-life-coach-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amanda%20Molenaar%20spent%20her%2020s%20and%2030s%20largely%20living%20abroad.%20Many%20of%20her%20friends%20from%20back%20home%20stayed%20close%20to%20where%20they%20grew%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Molenaar)%22%2C%22e