%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGas%20prices%20are%20at%20a%20four-year%20high%20in%20the%20US%20this%20Memorial%20Day.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENearly%2040%20million%20Americans%20will%20drive%20at%20least%2050%20miles%20from%20home%20during%20Memorial%20Day%20weekend.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMemorial%20Day%20weekend%20gas%20prices%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20reached%20a%20four-year%20high.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20largely%20the%20result%20of%20Trump's%20conflict%20with%20Iran.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20jaunt%20to%20the%20beach%20on%20Memorial%20Day%20will%20cost%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20national%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-gallon-us-aaa-highest-since-2022-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaverage%20for%20regular%20gas%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20%244.51%2C%20the%20highest%20it's%20been%20since%202022%2C%20when%20Russia%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20causing%20a%20spike%20in%20oil%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20price%20of%20gas%20is%204%20cents%20higher%20than%20a%20month%20ago%20and%20%241.32%20higher%20than%20the%20same%20time%20last%20year.%20As%20of%20Sunday%2C%20California%20has%20the%20highest%20average%20at%20%246.11%2C%20while%20Indiana%20has%20the%20lowest%20at%20%243.93.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMemorial%20Day%20marks%20the%20unofficial%20start%20of%20summer%2C%20and%20millions%20of%20Americans%20will%20travel%20to%20cookouts%2C%20parties%2C%20and%20vacation%20destinations%20to%20celebrate.%20AAA%20projects%20almost%2040%20million%20people%20will%20drive%20at%20least%2050%20miles%20from%20home%20between%20Thursday%20and%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat'll%20now%20cost%20over%20%24200%20in%20most%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTravel%20demand%20remains%20strong%2C%20and%20despite%20higher%20fuel%20prices%2C%20many%20people%20are%20prioritizing%20leisure%20travel%20during%20holiday%20breaks%2C%26quot%3B%20Stacey%20Barber%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20AAA%20Travel%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20summer's%20escalating%20prices%20are%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20US%20and%20Israel's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-war-with-iran-by-numbers-energy-drinks-to-targets-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewar%20on%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Iran%20all%20but%20closed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraffic-appears-to-halt-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStrait%20of%20Hormuz%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20waterway%20through%20which%20around%2020%25%20of%20the%20world's%20oil%20supply%20and%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20pass%20through%20%E2%80%94%20following%20those%20initial%20attacks.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20oil%20and%20gas%20prices%20have%20spiked%20worldwide%2C%20forcing%20some%20countries%20to%20enact%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-spike-what-countries-are-telling-people-to-do-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenergy-saving%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20a%20deal%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20to%20reopen%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20is%20%26quot%3Blargely%20negotiated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFinal%20aspects%20and%20details%20of%20the%20Deal%20are%20currently%20being%20discussed%2C%20and%20will%20be%20announced%20shortly%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post.%20%26quot%3BIn%20addition%20to%20many%20other%20elements%20of%20the%20Agreement%2C%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20will%20be%20opened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20comments%20sent%20oil%20prices%20sharply%20lower%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20week%2C%20with%20crude%20futures%20falling%20more%20than%205%25%20in%20early%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternational%20benchmark%20Brent%20crude%20fell%203.9%25%20to%20about%20%2499.50%20a%20barrel%20as%20of%209%3A40%20p.m.%20ET%20Sunday%2C%20while%20US%20West%20Texas%20Intermediate%20crude%20dropped%204.3%25%20to%20roughly%20%2492.50%20a%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20oil%20futures%20reacted%20immediately%20to%20Trump's%20statements%2C%20drivers%20may%20not%20see%20relief%20at%20the%20pump%20right%20away.%20Retail%20gasoline%20prices%20generally%20trail%20moves%20in%20crude%20oil%20prices%20because%20fuel%20purchased%20at%20earlier%2C%20higher%20wholesale%20costs%20can%20take%20time%20to%20work%20through%20the%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20remain%20volatile%2C%20with%20oil%20continuing%20to%20swing%20on%20geopolitical%20headlines%20tied%20to%20the%20conflict%20in%20Iran%2C%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20at%20this%20stage%20before%2C%20only%20for%20talks%20to%20break%20down.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20market%20will%20likely%20be%20more%20cautious%20about%20overreacting%20to%20these%20headlines%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Warren%20Patterson%2C%20the%20head%20of%20commodity%20strategy%20at%20ING%2C%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-memorial-day-weekend-travel-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779651026000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1347dd7ff506e273e67565%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-memorial-day-weekend-travel-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAA%20said%20Memorial%20Day%20weekend%20gas%20prices%20are%20the%20highest%20they've%20been%20in%20four%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds%2CHuileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20tells%20US%20negotiators%20'not%20to%20rush'%20into%20deal%