egrees%2C%20which%20is%20much%20colder%20than%20what%20we%20are%20used%20to%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wind%20in%20El%20Paso%20has%20also%20been%20challenging.%20We%20didn't%20do%20enough%20research%20before%20moving%2C%20especially%20about%20the%20neighborhood%20where%20we%20bought%20our%20home.%20It's%20a%20nice%2C%20brand-new%20neighborhood%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20open%20land%20behind%20us%2C%20so%20the%20wind%20feels%20even%20stronger.%20Just%20last%20week%2C%20winds%20reached%2041%20mph%2C%20tearing%20the%20curtains%20off%20our%20pergola.%20Dust%20storms%20are%20also%20common%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251b01165-439f-4242-bd6f-b40b114bc6f8%5C%22%3EWe're%20moving%20back%20to%20California%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20very%20sports-oriented%20and%20try%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20activities%20as%20a%20family.%20In%20California%2C%20we%20would%20go%20to%20Monterey%20Bay%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Dodger%20games%2C%20and%20other%20baseball%20games.%20But%20in%20El%20Paso%2C%20there%20just%20isn't%20as%20much%20to%20do%2C%20especially%20for%20a%2016-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20places%20to%20hike%2C%20but%20overall%2C%20it%20the%20activities%20here%20feel%20much%20more%20limited.%20I%20find%20myself%20looking%20forward%20to%20visiting%20places%20like%20San%20Francisco%2C%20Reno%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskip-las-vegas-visit-best-places-nevada-instead-local-recommendations-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELake%20Tahoe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Monterey%20Bay%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227625%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20Sacramento%2C%20California%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b6b55abc4e9d88574b2d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESacramento%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EDee%20Liu%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E