20felt%20nostalgic%2C%20and%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20spend%20time%20together%20as%20a%20group.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDiscovering%20new%20places%20and%20visiting%20old%20ones%20was%20a%20blast%2C%20too%2C%20and%20I%20wish%20we'd%20done%20this%20sooner.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20best%20friend%20and%20I%20leave%20a%20trail%20of%20sand%20from%20our%20day%20at%20the%20beach%20as%20we%20hurriedly%20run%20ahead%20of%20my%20parents%2C%20beach%20cruisers%20haphazardly%20parked%20outside%20the%20rental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20hide%20a%20disheveled%20Barbie%20doll%20named%20Trixie%20(a%20victim%20of%20a%20DIY%20haircut%20long%20ago)%2C%20somewhere%20hilariously%20unexpected%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20favorite%20pastime%20of%20ours%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20best%20part%20is%20the%20suspense%20while%20we%20await%20the%20discovery%2C%20which%20prompts%20uncontrollable%20laughter%20when%20my%20mom%20or%20dad%20finds%20Trixie%20posing%20in%20the%20microwave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20just%20one%20of%20our%20staple%20summer%20vacation%20antics%20that%20my%20best%20friend%20and%20I%20had%20been%20performing%20since%20meeting%20in%20the%20last%20two%20flute%20seats%20of%20band%20class%20at%2012%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%2030-plus%20years%2C%20and%20the%20only%20thing%20that's%20changed%20is%20that%20we're%20grown%20adults%20with%20careers%20and%20children%20(hers%3A%20human%2C%20mine%3A%20canine)%2C%20and%20we've%20swapped%20soda%20for%20cocktails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20I'm%20based%20in%20New%20York%20and%20she's%20in%20Texas%2C%20so%20we%20mostly%20only%20see%20each%20other%20once%20a%20year%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrip-with-mom-every-year-best-travel-tips-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Especially%20chosen%20annual%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20instead%20of%20relaxing%20in%20Jamaica%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-road-trip-utah-arizona-national-parks-tips-mistakes-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroad-tripping%20through%20Arizona%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20hijack%20a%20long%20weekend%20of%20my%20parents'%20monthlong%20vacation%20on%20the%20Florida%20Gulf%20Coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f264d39-9471-4b44-8960-5b036eb10aca%5C%22%3EThe%20trip%20was%20a%20reunion%2013%20years%20in%20the%20making%20that%20took%20us%20right%20back%20to%20the%20good%20old%20days%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223210%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20women%20in%20pool%20on%20floats%20in%20yard%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a036b557c7e83f26041ad7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222408%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20trip%20had%20all%20of%20the%20makings%20of%20a%20wholesome%20getaway.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Breedlove%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMom%20and%20Dad%2C%20both%20in%20their%20early%2070s%2C%20were%20happy%20to%20oblige%20and%20let%20us%2043-year-olds%20join%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20Erin%20was%20like%20a%20bonus%20daughter%20to%20my%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20she%20spent%20weeks%20on%20end%20at%20my%20house%20during%20summer%20break%2C%20never%20missed%20a%20Friday%20pizza%20night%2C%20and%20always%20joined%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-planned-family-trip-teens-loved-tips-belize-activities-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efamily%20vacations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20life%20taking%20us%20both%20to%20various%20corners%20of%20the%20world%2C%20it%20had%20been%2013%20years%20since%20they%20last%20saw%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20two%20teens%20smiling%20at%20beach%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a036a5c7c7e83f26041ad6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20family%20vacation%20felt%20really%20nostalgic%2C%20reminding%20us%20of%20trips%20we'd%20taken%20together%20in%20the%20past.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Breedlove%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20the%20opportunity%20arose%20to%20crash%20my%20parents'%20vacation%20in%20Siesta%20Key%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20make%20the%20reunion%20finally%20happen%20as%20our%20annual%20trip%2C%20leaning%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-international-trip-multiple-generations-mistakes-lessons-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emultigenerational%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20nostalgic%20flair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20of%20us%20brought%20along%20matching%20pool%20floats%20and%20all%20of%20our%20old%20shenanigans%2C%20including%20Trixie's%20understudy%2C%20Tricia%2C%20courtesy%20of%20Erin's%20young%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Barbie%20doll%20with%20deck%20of%20cards%20on%20table%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a036c1795396a3b6e417832%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20still%20hid%20a%20doll%20around%20the%20house%2C%20just%20like%20old%20times.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Breedlove%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20we%20arrived%2C%20it%20was%20just%20like%20our%20beach%20jaunts%20of%20yesteryear%2C%20all%20of%20us%20under%20one%20roof%20in%20a%20house%20rental%2C%20sharing%20meals%2C%20laughs%2C%20sunshine%2C%20and%20for%20Erin%20and%20me%2C%20a%20room%20with%20bunkbeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20morning%2C%20we%20chatted%20with%20my%20parents%20over%20coffee%20before%20hitting%20the%20beach%20to%20lounge%20and%20search%20for%20seashells%20like%20we%20used%20to%2C%20reminiscing%20about%20that%20one%20time%20my%20mom%20allowed%20us%20to%20bring%2092%20of%20them%20home%2C%20for%20some%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277943d2c-afbc-45af-a319-3763e44a32c8%5C%22%3EBetween%20the%20great%20company%20and%20mix%20of%20old%20and%20new%20favorites%2C%20we%20had%20an%20amazing%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20women%20with%20sunglasses%20smiling%20in%20selfie%20on%20beach%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a036c8258810e27922accb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20quality%20time%20together%20on%20the%20beach%20and%20in%20the%20house.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Breedlove%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDinners%20were%20spent%20listening%20to%20live%20music%20with%20a%20bowl%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinding-the-best-clam-chowder-in-boston-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclam%20chowder%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20our%20favorite%20haunt%2C%20the%20dollar-bill-ridden%20Siesta%20Key%20Oyster%20Bar%2C%20and%20discovering%20new%20spots%20like%20Casa%20Masa%2C%20where%20the%20margaritas%20on%20tap%20and%20housemade%20blue-corn%20tortilla%20chips%20still%20have%20me%20swooning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20we'd%20round%20out%20the%20evening%20with%20card%20games%20at%20the%20house%2C%20snickering%20around%20the%20dining%20table%20while%20we%20waited%20for%20my%20parents%20to%20notice%20Trixie%20hanging%20upside%20down%20from%20the%20light%20fixture%20above%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20little%20surprise%2C%20I%20organized%20a%20sunset%20beach%20picnic%20for%20us%20girls%2C%20and%20it%20was%20such%20a%20great%20way%20to%20share%20a%20memorable%20experience%20with%20my%20mom%20and%20best%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad%20picking%20us%20up%20for%20our%20ride%20home%20after%20we%20wined%20and%20dined%20on%20the%20beach%20was%20the%20nostalgic%20cherry%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222738%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20women%20having%20picnic%20on%20beach%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a036a5c7c7e83f26041ad6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221825%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20loved%20having%20a%20sunset%20picnic%20with%20my%20mom%20and%20best%20friend.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Breedlove%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20my%20career%20as%20a%20travel%20writer%20allows%20me%20to%20venture%20to%20far-flung%20places%20(sometimes%20with%20Erin%20in%20tow)%2C%20the%20slower%20pace%20and%20walk%20down%20memory%20lane%20with%20my%20parents%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsiesta-key-beach-florida-ranked-best-in-usa-photos-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESiesta%20Key%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20this%20one%20of%20the%20most%20fulfilling%20trips%20I've%20had%20in%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20back%20to%20basics%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20exact%20type%20of%20vacation%20I%20needed%2C%20with%20quality%20time%20well%20spent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20with%20a%20slew%20of%20special%20memories%20made%20with%20some%20of%20my%20favorite%20people%20all%20together%20in%20one%20place%2C%20and%20sure%20of%20one%20thing%3A%20We%20won't%20be%20going%20another%2013%20years%20before%20doing%20this%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacation-with-older-parents-best-friend-benefits-florida-multigenerational-trip-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779631321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a036a5c95396a3b6e417817%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacation-with-older-parents-best-friend-benefits-florida-multigenerational-trip-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20best%20friend%20and%20I%20are%20in%20our%2040s%2C%20and%20we%20had%20an%20amazing%20multigenerational%20beach%20vacation%20in%20Florida%20with%20my%20older%20parents%2C%20who%20are%20in%20their%2070s.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Breedlove)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%2