20fireplace%20%E2%80%94%20were%20given%20to%20Graham%20as%20promotional%20items%20from%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20could've%20been%20a%20%2410%2C000%20project%20only%20cost%20him%20about%20%243%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20spent%20around%20%241%2C500%20on%20a%20cowhide%20couch%20from%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20and%20%241%2C500%20on%20wood%20to%20make%20new%20cabinetry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20walls%20and%20ceiling%20of%20the%20renovated%20shed%20are%20especially%20impressive.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20shed%20after%20its%20renovations.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0f1829b1025a62a5c85941%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20the%20shed%20after%20its%20renovations.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Graham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20anybody%20steps%20into%20%5Bthe%20shed%5D%2C%20they're%20immediately%20drawn%20to%20the%20walls%20and%20ceiling%2C%20which%20are%20covered%20with%20whiskey%20barrels%20I%20deconstructed%2C%26quot%3B%20Graham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20barrel%20staves%20(the%20curved%20strips%20of%20wood%20used%20to%20craft%20the%20containers)%20to%20create%20a%203D%20woven%20effect%2C%20which%20adds%20warmth%20and%20texture%20to%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20received%20the%20materials%20from%20a%20distillery%20in%20Nashville%20that%20reached%20out%20to%20offer%20help%20when%20Graham%20first%20started%20posting%20about%20his%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20actually%20need%20a%20boatload%20of%20whiskey%20barrels.%26quot%3B%20They%20sent%20around%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20crazy%20experience%20because%20my%20neighbors%20were%20smelling%20whiskey%20a%20couple%20of%20houses%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20love%20Tennessee%20and%20being%20from%20Tennessee%2C%20so%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20character%20in%20pieces%20of%20the%20shed%20being%20derived%20from%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENow%2C%20Graham's%20man%20cave%20is%20the%20ideal%20space%20to%20have%20a%20cigar%2C%20enjoy%20some%20whiskey%2C%20or%20watch%20a%20Disney%20movie%20with%20his%20son.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tyler%20Graham%20enjoying%20a%20cigar%20and%20whiskey%20inside%20his%20man%20cave.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0f184eb1025a62a5c85943%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETyler%20Graham%20enjoying%20a%20cigar%20and%20whiskey%20inside%20his%20man%20cave.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Graham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20wasn't%20always%20easy%2C%20which%20makes%20Graham%20even%20prouder%20of%20the%20work%20he%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20multiple%20times%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20give%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20pretty%20stressful%20three%20months%2C%20because%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20do%20any%20of%20this%20stuff%20before.%20But%20it%20turned%20out%20way%20better%20than%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20going%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20uses%20the%20space%20to%20watch%20University%20of%20Tennessee%20football%20games%2C%20host%20friends%2C%20and%20relax%20when%20he%20gets%20some%20private%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20son%2C%20though%2C%20might%20be%20the%20man%20cave's%20biggest%20fan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20used%20%5Bthe%20shed%5D%20more%20as%20a%20Disney%20movie%20theater%20with%20my%20son%20than%20I%20have%20as%20a%20whiskey%20and%20cigar%20lounge%2C%26quot%3B%20Graham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-turns-tool-shed-into-backyard-man-cave-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779626761000%2C%22visu