20in%2015%20minutes%20of%20work%20when%20I'm%2C%20say%2C%20waiting%20at%20the%20car%20wash.%20My%20phone%20is%20always%20in%20my%20hand%20for%20all%20kinds%20of%20reasons%2C%20most%20especially%20so%20I'm%20available%20to%20my%20kids%20in%20case%20of%20an%20emergency.%20I'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenthood-constant-work-no-downtime-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enever%20really%20off%20duty%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20yes%2C%20I'm%20also%20just%20plain%20tech-addled%2C%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20I%20boarded%20Canyon%20Spirit%20%E2%80%94%20a%20luxury%20train%20journey%20through%20the%20American%20West%20built%20specifically%20around%20slowing%20down%20and%20embracing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnail-mail-club-handwritten-letters-analog-hobby-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalog%20pleasures%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20be%20a%20novelty%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20drinking%20a%20colorful%20drink%20on%20the%20train.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a10598851ede568c7e17568%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20staring%20at%20the%20gorgeous%20scenery....while%20worrying%20about%20what%20was%20happening%20at%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a635667-50a5-4cb5-b5b8-f23c5240979d%5C%22%3EThere%20was%20no%20WiFi%20on%20board%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trip%20stretches%20across%20three%20days%20and%20was%20intentionally%20designed%20to%20encourage%20presence.%20There's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstayed-at-resort-limited-wifi-loved-unplugging-abroad-india-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20WiFi%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20board%2C%20entirely%20by%20design.%20The%20assignment%20is%20to%20unplug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20me%20under%20the%20best%20circumstances.%20I'm%20not%20someone%20naturally%20predisposed%20toward%20digital%20detoxes%2C%20but%20I%20was%20optimistic%20the%20setting%20would%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20my%20train%20window%2C%20snowy%20mountain%20landscapes%20in%20Colorado%20slowly%20gave%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Futah-national-parks-ranked-from-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUtah's%20red%20rock%20canyons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20Colorado%20River%20winding%20for%20hours%20alongside%20us.%20It%20was%20totally%20serene%2C%20with%20meals%20and%20drinks%20served%20right%20at%20our%20seats%20and%20domed%20glass%20railcars%20for%20panoramic%20vistas%20from%20every%20angle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20an%20objectively%20terrible%20time%20for%20me%20to%20be%20unreachable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20in%20front%20of%20a%20sign%20that%20says%20Arches%20National%20Park.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1059cab1025a62a5c85f46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20trip%20included%20visits%20to%20national%20parks.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225569c181-1c22-46cc-9e84-aa6f2fd65d25%5C%22%3EIt%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20comically%20bad%20time%20to%20unplug%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-how-to-negotiate-best-price-down-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enegotiate%20an%20offer%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20potential%20new%20home%20back%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20We%20were%20trying%20to%20go%20back%20and%20forth%20with%20DocuSign%20contracts%20and%20nuanced%20discussions%20about%20contingencies%20on%20what%20might%20be%20the%20biggest%20purchase%20of%20our%20entire%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20were%20also%20dealing%20with%20unrelated%20drama%20involving%20our%20current%20house%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mess%20that%20required%20keeping%20detailed%20communications%20logs%20for%20a%20potential%20future%20legal%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20because%20there%20was%20apparently%20still%20a%20bit%20more%20room%20for%20maximum%20chaos%2C%20my%20son%20came%20down%20with%20a%20fever%20and%20vomiting%20back%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20my%20husband%20wasn't%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-dad-sobriety-cooking-for-family-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolo%20parenting%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20I%20was%20out%20of%20town%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20solo%20parenting%20a%20sick%20child%20(and%20doing%20all%20the%20unpleasant%20laundry%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20that)%20while%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20other%20child%20across%20town%20to%20school%E2%80%A6%20and%20simultaneously%20juggling%20all%20the%20other%20circuslike%20logistics%20of%20this%20utterly%20chaotic%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20leaning%20out%20of%20the%20window%20of%20the%20train.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1059f47ff506e273e66797%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20checked%20in%20at%20home%20when%20possible%2C%20but%20still%20managed%20to%20enjoy%20her%20trip.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alesandra%20Dubin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20awful%20about%20the%20timing%20of%20my%20trip%2C%20and%20threw%20on%20an%20extremely%20generous%20helping%20of%20guilt%20and%20worry%20for%20good%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20I%20was%20aboard%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-train-vacation-popular-wealthy-travelers-orient-express-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20train%3C%2Fa%3E%20designed%20for%20leisurely%20observation%20and%20reflection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20while%20others%20were%20stepping%20onto%20the%20open-air%20observation%20deck%20to%20admire%20dramatic%20scenery%20and%20breathe%20in%20fresh%20mountain%20air%2C%20I%20was%20frequently%20out%20there%20for%20a%20different%20purpose%3A%20holding%20my%20phone%20toward%20the%20sky%20and%20trying%20to%20get%20my%20T-Mobile%20satellite%20feature%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20suspect%20this%20wasn't%20exactly%20the%20intended%20use%20case%20for%20those%20spectacular%20observation%20decks%2C%20so%20unique%20to%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20particular%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed540899-0519-4966-b54c-88894a32f74f%5C%22%3EThough%20I%20didn't%20fully%20unplug%2C%20it%20was%20still%20a%20good%20trip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20still%2C%20after%20all%20this%2C%20I%20actually%20don't%20think%20the%20trip%20was%20a%20failure%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20I%20absolutely%20did%20not%20return%20home%20from%20my%20trip%20transformed%20into%20a%20person%20who%20suddenly%20wants%20to%20disappear%20into%20the%20wilderness%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-off-grid-vs-van-life-pros-cons-benefits-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20off%20the%20grid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20will%20never%20be%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20didn't%20fully%20unplug%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20OK.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20contest%2C%20and%20it's%20simply%20not%20possible%20for%20some%20people.%20I%20checked%20in%20as%20much%20as%20I%20could%2C%20given%20the%20circumstances%2C%20and%20handled%20what%20I%20could%20remotely.%20When%20I%20had%20pockets%20of%20connectivity%2C%20I%20provided%20updates%20on%20my%20next%20expected%20WiFi%20patch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yes%2C%20I%20still%20worried.%20I%20still%20felt%20guilty%20about%20everything%20unfolding%20back%20at%20home.%20But%20being%20somewhere%20that%20removed%20some%20of%20my%20usual%20options%20changed%20the%20rhythm%20of%20my%20days%20in%20a%20few%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20many%20stages%2C%20I%20just%20accepted%20that%20connection%20was%20out%20of%20the%20realm%20of%20possibility%2C%20and%20I%20found%20myself%20sitting%20quietly%20and%20staring%20out%20the%20window%20longer%20than%20I%20normally%20would.%20I%20noticed%20all%20those%20dramatically%20changing%20colors%20in%20the%20landscape.%20I%20caught%20the%20resonant%2C%20intoxicating%20smell%20of%20pine%20in%20higher%20elevations.%20I%20exchanged%20perspectives%20with%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmade-friend-on-international-flight-became-pen-pals-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efellow%20travelers%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20meals%20and%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20the%20lesson%20was%20just%20that%20there%20was%20value%20in%20being%20forced%20%E2%80%94%20however%20reluctantly%20%E2%80%94%20to%20loosen%20my%20grip%20for%20a%20little%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20although%20I%20couldn't%20do%20much%20about%20the%20stress%20waiting%20for%20me%20back%20home%2C%20I%20got%20to%20carry%20it%20through%20red-rock%20canyons%20and%20snow-covered%20mountains%20instead%20of%20through%20another%20ordinary%20week%20of%20multitasking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-solo-train-trip-no-wifi-worst-time-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779625141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1059427ff506e273e66789%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-solo-train-trip-no-wifi-worst-time-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20went%20on%20a%203-day%20trip%20without%20WiFi%20designed%20to%20unplug.%20It%20was%20a%20bad%20time%20to%20do%20it%20%E2%80%94%20we%20were%20negot