an%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveled-solo-for-decade-best-tips-make-friends-stay-safe-2025-9%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esolo%20trips%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I've%20had%20strangers%20help%20me%20get%20my%20van%20out%20of%20mud%20and%20share%20meals%20with%20me.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20two%20years%20of%20traveling%2C%20my%20adventures%20have%20reminded%20me%20of%20how%20kind%20people%20can%20be.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20excursion%20in%20my%20newly%20purchased%20camper%20van%20%E2%80%94%20a%20one-night%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseveral-national-parks-one-road-trip-tips-mistakes-month-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20a%20national%20forest%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20hours%20from%20my%20home%20%E2%80%94%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20debacle.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trip%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20test%20run%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-feel-safe-as-woman-on-solo-van-trip-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esolo%20van%20living%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20I%20fully%20took%20the%20plunge%2C%20and%20it%20certainly%20did%20test%20me.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dispersed%20campsite%20was%20full%20of%20deceivingly%20deep%20mud%2C%20and%20my%20van%20got%20stuck%20in%20it.%20After%20unsuccessfully%20trying%20to%20get%20out%2C%20I%20asked%20the%20next%20site%20over%20for%20help.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20pushed%20and%20shoved%20without%20success%20and%20offered%20to%20drive%20me%20around%20to%20find%20someone%20with%20a%20truck%20who%20could%20tow%20me%20out.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20a%20group%20of%20retirees%20also%20offered%20to%20help%2C%20and%20I%20was%20soon%20in%20the%20passenger%20seat%20of%20a%20little%20red%20truck.%20We%20were%20about%2015%20yards%20from%20my%20van%20when%20the%20truck%20slid%20to%20a%20halt%20in%20the%20mud.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20sun%20starting%20to%20fade%20between%20the%20pine%20trees%2C%20it%20was%20looking%20like%20we'd%20both%20be%20stuck%20for%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20worry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20assured%20me%20as%20he%20headed%20back%20to%20his%20campsite.%20%26quot%3BMy%20buddy%20has%20a%20bigger%20truck%20and%20is%20coming%20up%20tomorrow.%20He'll%20tow%20both%20of%20us%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%201%20a.m.%2C%20I%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20a%20fist%20pounding%20on%20my%20door%20and%20a%20gruff%20voice%20yelling%2C%20%26quot%3BSheriff's%20office!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20scolding%20for%20getting%20myself%20into%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20officer%20towed%20my%20van%20out%20and%20explained%20that%20someone%20had%20called%20911%20for%20a%20wellness%20check%20after%20they%20saw%20the%20red%20truck%20drive%20me%20back%20to%20my%20campsite%20and%20never%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20drove%20my%20newly%20liberated%20van%20back%20down%20the%20road%2C%20I%20passed%20the%20group%20who%20had%20first%20helped%20me%3A%20A%20bunch%20of%20strangers%20who%20had%20gone%20out%20of%20their%20way%20%E2%80%94%20including%20driving%20to%20get%20cell%20service%20to%20call%20911%20%E2%80%94%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20was%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20embarrassed%20by%20just%20how%20many%20people%20I'd%20dragged%20into%20this%20fiasco%2C%20but%20also%20overwhelmed%20with%20gratitude.%20It%20was%20an%20important%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-off-grid-vs-van-life-pros-cons-benefits-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elesson%20of%20van%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20There%20are%20often%20people%20looking%20out%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22641a528f-b66a-47d3-9a2b-a6eaae9d545e%5C%22%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20experienced%20even%20more%20kindness%20while%20traveling%20in%20my%20van%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Van%20parked%20in%20wooded%20are%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1065967ff506e273e66830%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22624%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI'm%20still%20grateful%20to%20those%20who%20helped%20me%20get%20my%20van%20out%20of%20the%20mud.%3Cp%3ESydnee%20Chapman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20escapade%20in%20that%20Utah%20forest%20was%20far%20from%20the%20last%20time%20I'd%20experience%20kindness%20from%20strangers%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20parked%20next%20to%20a%20family%20friend's%20vacation%20cabin%20on%20Washington%20Island%2C%20some%20curious%20neighbors%20wandered%20over%20to%20see%20my%20rig.%20The%20couple%2C%20who%20were%20my%20grandparents'%20age%2C%20explained%20they'd%20also%20had%20their%20own%20taste%20of%20van%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20love%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-traveler-meetups-women-of-color-who-travel-south-asian-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emeeting%20other%20travelers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20told%20me%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20I%20needed%20anything%20to%20swing%20by%20their%20cabin%20a%20few%20houses%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20became%20a%20sort%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneighbor-became-surrogate-grandmother-to-kids-best-friend-for-me-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadopted%20set%20of%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20next%20week%2C%20inviting%20me%20over%20for%20dinner%20and%20sending%20me%20home%20with%20leftovers%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20place%20to%20shower%2C%20and%20making%20sure%20my%20van%20was%20warm%20enough%20for%20the%20cool%20September%20nights.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20husband%2C%20a%20certified%20MacGyver%20type%2C%20showed%20me%20how%20to%20fix%20my%20sink%20after%20I%20admitted%20it%20had%20been%20out%20of%20service%20for%20about%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20been%20anything%20resembling%20an%20extrovert%2C%20but%20my%20%26quot%3Bgrandparents%26quot%3B%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20sort%20of%20experience%20we%20miss%20out%20on%20when%20we%20retreat%20into%20ourselves%20rather%20than%20welcome%20in%20those%20around%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224657%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20in%20van%20in%20Joshua%20Tree%20desert%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a10659651ede568c7e17612%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223287%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI've%20taken%20my%20van%20to%20places%20like%20Joshua%20Tree.%3Cp%3ESydnee%20Chapman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20the%20only%20mechanic%20who%20could%20see%20me%20when%20my%20AC%20stopped%20working%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-new-year-at-joshua-tree-lucky-to-exist-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJoshua%20Tree%3C%2Fa%3E%20desert%20pleasantly%20surprised%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20nowhere%20to%20go%20while%20he%20worked%20on%20my%20van%2C%20we%20chatted%20about%20life%2C%20religion%2C%20and%20the%20difficulty%20of%20starting%20over.%20It%20was%20the%20kind%20of%20conversation%20most%20of%20us%20have%20with%20a%20close%20friend%20rather%20than%20a%20stranger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20told%20him%20that%20cars%20have%20been%20somewhat%20of%20a%20foreign%20language%20to%20me%20most%20of%20my%20life%2C%20he%20began%20explaining%20what%20he%20was%20doing%2C%20helping%20me%20get%20hands-on%20while%20pointing%20out%20things%20I%20could%20repair%20on%20my%20own%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1b15f22-20d8-4be5-88e1-ad8c1c1bf32a%5C%22%3EThese%20kinds%20of%20human%20connections%20are%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20things%20about%20travel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22van%20driving%20in%20death%20valley%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1065967ff506e273e6682f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVan%20life%20isn't%20always%20easy%2C%20but%20I've%20met%20some%20kind%20strangers%20along%20the%20way.%3Cp%3ESydnee%20Chapman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20we're%20increasingly%20isolated%20and%20glued%20to%20our%20phones%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffull-time-van-life-love-despite-cons-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evan%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20restored%20my%20faith%20in%20humanity.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20I've%20met%20so%20many%20strangers%20who%20have%20shown%20me%20that%20there%20are%20still%20great%20people%20out%20there%20willing%20to%20lend%20a%20hand%20if%20you're%20willing%20to%20open%20yourself%20up%20to%20new%20connections%20and%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20dreamed%20of%20doing%20solo%20van%20life%20since%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20often%20questioning%20whether%20I%20was%20capable%20enough%20to%20go%20on%20the%20adventure%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I'd%20spent%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-woman-travel-safety-tips-frequent-international-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraveling%20solo%20internationally%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20living%20by%20myself%2C%20something%20about%20being%20on%20the%20road%2C%20especially%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20with%20nothing%20more%20than%20my%20own%20wits%20to%20keep%20me%20company%20seemed%20like%20a%20different%20beast%20entirely.%20Imagined%20kidnappers%20and%20bad%20actors%20lurked%20in%20my%20head%20constantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20still%20very%20important%20to%20follow%20safety%20protocols%20be%20vigilant%20while%20on%20the%20road%20since%20encountering%20those%20possible%20dangers%20(and%20others)%20isn't%20out%20of%20the%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20though%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20the%20world%20isn't%20as%20scary%20of%20a%20place%20as%20we%20often%20make%20it%20out%20to%20be.%20Yes%2C%20there%20are%20bad%20people%20out%20there