or%20of%20a%20double-decker%20Amtrak%20Superliner%20train%20with%20red%20and%20blue%20stripes%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699777f9e1ba468a96ac5820%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBusiness%20Insider%20will%20do%20a%20few%20things%20differently%20the%20next%20time%20she%20rides%20the%20California%20Zephyr.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20took%20Amtrak's%20California%20Zephyr%20train%20from%20Chicago%20to%20California%20in%20February%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%2053%20hours%2C%20it's%20the%20longest%20train%20ride%20in%20the%20US.%20I%20booked%20a%20%242%2C200%20bedroom%20for%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20want%20to%20ride%20the%20California%20Zephyr%20again%2C%20but%20I'll%20pack%20differently%20and%20board%20at%20a%20different%20stop.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20exited%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-california-zephyr-bedroom-tour%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20Zephyr%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Emeryville%20after%20a%2053-hour%20journey%20from%20Chicago%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-california-zephyr-overnight-train-surprises%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elongest%20train%20ride%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20I%20knew%20I'd%20be%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20the%20time%20of%20my%20life%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F30-hour-amtrak-train-overnight-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eovernight%20Amtrak%20train%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%202026.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-bedrooms-superliner-vs-viewliner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebooked%20a%20bedroom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20essentially%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-home-hotel-slube-germany-surprising-things%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etiny%20hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20room%2C%20for%20%242%2C200.%20And%20I%20enjoyed%20it%20so%20much%20that%20I'm%20certain%20I'll%20take%20the%20California%20Zephyr%20again.%20But%20there%20are%20a%20few%20things%20I'll%20do%20differently%20next%20time%20to%20save%20money%20and%20make%20the%20most%20of%20my%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'll%20pack%20lighter.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20packed%20bags%20in%20front%20of%20a%20couch%20in%20an%20Amtrak%20bedroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0c72e0f246b392afc7b647%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20two-night%20journey%20on%20the%20California%20Zephyr%20was%20part%20of%20a%20weeklong%20trip%2C%20so%20I%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-with-backpack-vs-carry-on-luggage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebackpack%20and%20a%20carry-on%20suitcase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20I%20kept%20with%20me%20in%20my%2050-square-foot%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brought%20some%20items%20exclusively%20for%20the%20train%20ride%2C%20including%20my%20ukulele.%20I%20imagined%20passing%20the%20time%20by%20learning%20songs%20and%20writing%20new%20ones%2C%20but%20with%20thin%20walls%20between%20guests%2C%20I%20decided%20against%20playing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20brought%20my%20own%20towel%20and%20shower%20toiletries%2C%20but%20my%20bedroom%20provided%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'll%20leave%20all%20of%20these%20items%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'll%20bring%20binoculars.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20train%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20a%20snowy%20mountain%20scene%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0cacf7be2e5e1daf890a31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20Rockies%20to%20the%20Sierra%20Nevada%20mountains%2C%20the%20California%20Zephyr%20is%20the%20most%20scenic%20Amtrak%20journey%20I've%20ever%20been%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rails%20go%20through%20the%20wilderness%20across%20the%20diverse%20landscapes%20of%20the%20American%20West.%20The%20best%20place%20to%20catch%20the%20views%20is%20undoubtedly%20the%20observation%20car%2C%20a%20communal%20lounge%20car%20with%20two%20rows%20of%20wide%20windows%20on%20each%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20stared%20out%20the%20windows%20in%20awe%2C%20I%20longed%20for%20a%20closer%20look.%20With%20binoculars%2C%20I%20might%20have%20spotted%20more%20wildlife%20or%20noticed%20more%20textural%20details%20in%20the%20trees%2C%20rocks%2C%20rivers%2C%20and%20canyons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'll%20go%20during%20a%20different%20time%20of%20year.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227681%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fall%20colors%20start%20peaking%20on%20Kenosha%20Pass%20in%20Park%20County%2C%20Colorado%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0c75a7f246b392afc7b66f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225120%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMountains%20near%20Denver%20pictured%20in%20the%20fall.%3Cp%3EHyoung%20Chang%2FThe%20Denver%20Post%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I've%20seen%20the%20full%20route%20in%20winter%2C%20next%20time%20I%20want%20to%20visit%20during%20a%20different%20season%20for%20a%20fresh%20view%20of%20the%20passing%20landscape.%20I'd%20love%20to%20see%20what%20it's%20like%20in%20September%20or%20October%20for%20peak%20fall%20foliage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'll%20try%20different%20menu%20items.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Empty%20Amtrak%20dining%20tables%20in%20front%20of%20windows%20showing%20mountains%20outside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02087fba7ef34b41f37075%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmtrak%20sleeping%20accommodation%20tickets%20include%20meals%20on%20board.%20Three%20days%20and%20two%20nights%20weren't%20enough%20time%20to%20try%20all%20the%20menu%20items%20in%20the%20dining%20car.%20And%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20good%20the%20dishes%20I%20ordered%20were%2C%20from%20the%20grilled%20chicken%20Caesar%20salad%20to%20the%20steak%20dinner%20and%20cheesecake%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I%20want%20to%20get%20the%20breakfast%20quesadilla%2C%20the%20burger%2C%20and%20the%20grilled%20patty%20melt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'll%20skip%20the%20first%2020-or-so%20hours.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20plains%20as%20the%20sun%20sets%20out%20the%20window%20of%20a%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe3824e1443b8dc48e3645%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20experienced%20the%20full%20route%20of%20the%20California%20Zephyr.%20Still%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20the%20views%20on%20the%20first%20day%20are%20the%20least%20dramatic%20of%20the%20trip%20as%20you%20travel%20west%20through%20the%20plains%20of%20Illinois%20and%20into%20Iowa%20and%20Nebraska.%20Once%20you%20hit%20Colorado%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20day%20two%2C%20you're%20flush%20with%20breathtaking%20views%20for%20most%20of%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20on%20in%20Denver%20for%20a%20shorter%20trip%20would%20save%20me%20money%20without%20sacrificing%20the%20best%20views.%20When%20searching%20for%20future%20trip%20dates%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20trip%20from%20Denver%20was%20listed%20for%20half%20the%20pri