%202026%20lands%20on%20Monday%2C%20May%2025.%20For%20many%2C%20this%20means%20a%20blissful%20three-day%20weekend%20from%20work%20or%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd5e2ae5-777c-45c1-b45b-25b35aea19b9%5C%22%3EWhen%20do%20Memorial%20Day%20sales%20end%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20difficult%20to%20say%20exactly%20when%20all%20sales%20will%20end.%20As%20a%20rule%20of%20thumb%2C%20I%20always%20advise%20shopping%20before%20Memorial%20Day%20itself%2C%20since%20few%20retailers%20promise%20to%20continue%20discounts%20beyond%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20select%20few%20stores%20(mainly%20mattress%20and%20furniture%20brands)%20will%20continue%20their%20promotions%20through%20early%20this%20week%2C%20so%20late%20readers%20may%20still%20have%20luck%20scoring%20a%20price%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6a84749-f2cd-424b-86c8-c9892f818bc9%5C%22%3EWhat%20about%20Amazon%20Prime%20Day%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20announced%20its%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Famazon-prime-day%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrime%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20returning%20in%20June%2C%20but%20has%20yet%20to%20specify%20exact%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20wondering%20whether%20it's%20worth%20waiting%20until%20then%20to%20shop%2C%20your%20instinct%20isn't%20entirely%20wrong.%20It's%20true%3A%20many%20items%20will%20be%20down%20to%20all-time%20lows%20for%20the%20event%2C%20marking%20huge%20savings%20on%20vacuums%2C%20Apple%20tech%2C%20beauty%20products%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Amazon%20Prime%20Day%20is%20exclusive%20only%20to%20that%20single%20retailer.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20you%20can't%20find%20smaller%20businesses%2C%20DTC%20mattress%20brands%2C%20or%20exclusive%20style%20companies%20on%20sale%20for%20the%20event.%20Memorial%20Day%20is%20still%20an%20excellent%20chance%20to%20save%20big%20from%20stores%20across%20the%20board%2C%20so%20I%20recommend%20jumping%20on%20these%20deals%20while%20you%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESee%20more%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fmemorial-day-mattress-sales-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMemorial%20Day%20mattress%20deals%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%7C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Famazon-memorial-day-deals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAmazon%20Memorial%20Day%20deals%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%7C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fsaatva-memorial-day-sale-deals-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ESaatva%20Memorial%20Day%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%7C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fsleep-number-memorial-day-sale-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ESleep%20Number%20Memorial%20Day%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%7C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fleesa-memorial-day-mattress-sale-deals-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ELeesa%20Memorial%20Day%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%7C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fwayfair-memorial-day-outdoor-furniture-deals-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EWayfair%20Memorial%20Day%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFollow%20our%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Vb2J5x9J3juulcffA60F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EWhatsApp%20channel%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20on%20mobile%20for%20more%20buying%20guides%2C%20deals%2C%20and%20reviews.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20origina