20with%20AI%20bots%20like%20Claude%20or%20Lovable%20and%20instructing%20them%20to%20build%20apps%20and%20websites%2C%20often%20without%20writing%20a%20single%20line%20of%20code%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20how%20these%20three%20people%20made%20it%20happen%20%E2%80%94%20and%20stay%20tuned%20for%20more%20stories%20in%20this%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirefighter-vibe-coded-app-to-make-grocery-shopping-easier-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoe%20Poynton%2C%20a%2044-year-old%20firefighter%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20grew%20frustrated%20by%20having%20to%20double%20back%20through%20grocery%20stores%20after%20forgetting%20items%20on%20his%20shopping%20list.%20Rather%20than%20accepting%20the%20frustration%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20AI%20tools%20to%20build%20an%20app%20that%20optimizes%20shopping%20routes%20based%20on%20how%20users%20move%20through%20a%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmorgasburg-founder-vibe-coded-app-building-home-ai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJonathan%20Butler%2C%20a%2056-year-old%20entrepreneur%20in%20Brooklyn%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20building%20a%20home%20in%20upstate%20New%20York.%20He%20expects%20it%20to%20take%2018-24%20months%20and%20will%20require%20blueprints%2C%20contracts%2C%20drawings%2C%20and%20photographs.%20Those%20all%20too%20easily%20get%20lost%2C%20so%20he%20vibe-coded%20a%20personalized%20document-sharing%20platform%20with%20his%20architect%20and%20contractor.%20It's%20not%20perfect%2C%20he%20says%2C%20and%20he's%20constantly%20refining%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20being%20in%20your%20wood%20shop%20making%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20used%20to%20feel%20%26quot%3Bso%20powerless%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20couldn't%20build%20his%20own%20websites.%20Now%2C%20he%20feels%20empowered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScott%20Kippler%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20a%20hedge%20fund%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20had%20to%20juggle%20work%20while%20also%20getting%20his%20son%20from%20school%20and%20taking%20him%20to%20an%20after-school%20program.%20Instead%20of%20scouring%20Facebook%20groups%20for%20a%20part-time%20helper%2C%20he%20vibe-coded%20a%20solution.%20In%20a%20week%2C%20he%20created%20a%20preliminary%20model%20of%20Trot%20My%20Tot%2C%20a%20platform%20where%20parents%20can%20find%20short-term%20nannies%20for%20one-off%20gigs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20vibe-coding%3F%20Tell%20me%20your%20story%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asrussolillo%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esrussolillo%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20And%20be%20sure%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20our%20weekly%20newsletter%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fvibe-mode%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVibe%20Mode%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20where%20we%20chronicle%20all%20things%20vibe-coding%2C%20the%20new%20AI%20builder%20economy%2C%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20world%2C%20from%20careers%20to%20markets.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-sunday-newsletter-vibe-coding-ai-tools-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779618961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a10bacdb1025a62a5c86678%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-sunday-newsletter-vibe-coding-ai-tools-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20this%20Sunday%20edition%20of%20Business%20Insider%20Today%2C%20these%20three%20non-techie%20people%20vibe-coded%20solutions%20to%20their%20problems.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22srussolillo%40insider.com%20(Steve%20Russolillo)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BBC%20at%20the%20site%20of%20China's%20worst%20mining%20disaster%20in%20more%20than%20a%20decade%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779618892000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F77b2%2Flive%2F14f6e760-5758-11f1-b682-cf91850925ea.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc809m33yjz7o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2082%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20after%20a%20gas%20explosion%20at%20the%20Liushenyu%20mine%20in%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc809m33yjz7o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22McKinsey%20wants%20job%20candidates%20to%20practice%20interviews%20with%20AI%2C%20not%20pricey%20coaches%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223011%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McKinsey%20logo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01fbc9c9dd4cb81cda92ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222007%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoan%20Cros%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMcKinsey%20has%20built%20an%20AI-preparation%20tool%20for%20its%20interview%20candidates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20firm%20is%20offering%20applicants%20%26quot%3Bunlimited%26quot%3B%20attempts%20at%20the%20quantitative%20case%20study.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20McKinsey%20talent%20leader%20said%20it%20would%20help%20level%20the%20playing%20field%20for%20those%20who%20can't%20afford%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMcKinsey%20candidates%20can%20now%20practice%20their%20problem-solving%20for%20interviews%20with%20AI%20before%20they%20face%20the%20real%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%20global%20consulting%20firm%20launched%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-is-changing-consulting-talent-at-mckinsey-pwc-deloitte-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehelp%20candidates%20prepare%20for%20interviews%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20ideally%2C%20keep%20them%20from%20feeling%20they%20need%20to%20pay%20for%20pricey%20consulting%20coaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20is%20available%20globally%20to%20those%20applying%20for%20entry-level%20positions%20at%20the%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20business%20analyst%20and%20associate%20roles%2C%20Marie%20Christine%20Padberg%2C%20McKinsey's%20global%20talent%20attraction%20co-leader%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20practice%20tool%20gives%20applicants%20unlimited%20attempts%20at%20the%20quantitative%20case%20study%20they'll%20face%20in%20their%20interview%2C%20a%20hypothetical%20business%20scenario%20similar%20to%20work%20they%20might%20do%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-consulting-mckinsey-pwc-deloitte-bcg-kpmg-accenture-ey-ibm-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMcKinsey%20consultants%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPadberg%20said%20the%20tool%20helps%20McKinsey%20%26quot%3Bdemocratize%26quot%3B%20preparation%20by%20giving%20everybody%20the%20same%20starting%20point%20and%20access%20to%20the%20full%20range%20of%20preparation%20at%20no%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20receives%20about%20one%20million%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20annually%20and%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-hired-top-consulting-firms-bcg-mckinsey-pwc-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egiven%20jobs%20to%20around%201%25%20of%20applicants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcKinsey%20has%20long%20offered%20candidates%20preparation%20materials%2C%20including%20sample%20cases%2C%20video%20explainers%2C%20and%20guidance%20from%20current%20employees%20on%20what%20to%20expect.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20however%2C%20a%20cottage%20industry%20tailored%20to%20helping%20competitive%20young%20candidates%20land%20jobs%20at%20firms%20like%20McKinsey%2C%20Bain%2C%20and%20BCG%20has%20also%20grown%20alongside%20the%20official%20channels.%20Courses%20and%20preparation%20support%20can%20range%20from%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20to%20over%20%242%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPadberg%20said%20the%20firm%20has%20had%20issues%20with%20services%20misdirecting%20candidates%2C%20most%20commonly%20by%20overpreparing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20over-prepared%20people.%20We%20want%20to%20really%20get%20to%20the%20depth%20of%20a%20person's%20skills%20and%20capabilities%20through%20a%20connection%20and%20a%20conversation%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20want%20over-rehearsed%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1250fb6-c870-45d4-97ac-f93befaba6c2%5C%22%3EThe%20problem-solving%20case%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20offered%20an%20interview%20after%20initial%20screening%2C%20candidates%20will%20receive%20access%20to%20a%20preparation%20website%2C%20which%20helps%20ready%20them%20for%20both%20the%20personal%20interview%20and%20the%20problem-solving%20interview%20they%20face%20in%20the%20next%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20April%2C%20they%20may%20have%20had%20only%20three%20or%20four%20practice%20cases.%20Now%20they%20have%20unlimited%20chances%20to%20drill%20the%20case%20questions%20and%20math.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222234%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McKinsey%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01ef70c9dd4cb81cda924c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222085%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20tab%20on%20the%20website%20takes%20candidates%20to%20the%20AI%20prep%20tool.%3Cp%3EMcKinsey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOffering%20examples%20across%2015%20industries%2C%20the%20tool%20%E2%80%94%20which%20appears%20as%20a%20pop-up%20tab%20on%20the%20website%20%E2%80%94%20generates%20a%20new%20case-style%20question%20each%20time%20candidates%20use%20it.%20It%20starts%20with%20a%20brief%20client%20scenario%20and%20the%20figures%20needed%20to%20answer%20the%20question.%20Candidates%20can%20type%20in%20their%20answer%2C%20then%20reveal%20the%20correct%20response%20and%20see%20the%20calculation%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20month%2C%2010%2C000%20people%20have%20used%20the%20AI%20assistant%2C%20said%20Padberg.%20McKinsey%20does%20not%20track%20how%20candidates%20use%20it%2C%20nor%20does%20it%20capture%20how%20good%20their%20answers%20are%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222479%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McKinsey%20AI%20prep%20tool%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0c585dd0fd55e72b67bcf4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223508%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20case%20study%20example%20on%20the%20AI%20Prep%20Tool.%3Cp%3EMcKinsey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quantitative%20component%20is%20especially%20important%2C%20she%20said%2C%20because%20even%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-ai-agents-mangement-leadership-great-flattening-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-enabled%20workplace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20consultants%20still%20need%20to%20understand%20how%20numbers%20connect%20and%20what%20they%20mean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20also%20addresses%20a%20very%20human%20part%20of%20the%20interview%20process%3A%20nerves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20element%20that%20people%20often%20get%20quite%20nervous%20about%20because%20doing%20quantitative%20things%20is%20one%20thing%2C%20but%20doing%20it%20while%20somebody's%20watching%20you%20is%20something%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279c22b7c-065b-406c-8d68-9cf3a72613c1%5C%22%3ERecruiting%20for%20the%20AI%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20professional%20services%2C%20firms%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20automate%20some%20of%20the%20more%20tedious%20work%20that%20junior%20employees%20once%20handled%2C%20from%20research%20to%20first-draft%20analysis%2C%20while%20placing%20greater%20emphasis%20on%20judgment%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20work%20with%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKPMG%20has%20said%20it%20wants%20junior%20consultants%20increasingly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-big-four-junior-consultants-manage-teams-ai-agents-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanaging%20AI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20doing%20all%20the%20grunt%20work%20themselves.%20Dan%20Diasio%2C%20EY's%20global%20consulting%20AI%20leader%2C%20recently%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20AI%20is%20making%20junior%20consultants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fey-big-four-junior-consultants-valuable-skills-for-ai-age-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20creative%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turning%20them%20into%20%26quot%3Bcreators%20of%20new%20business%20models%2C%20creators%20of%20new%20opportunities%20for%20our%20clients%2C%20creators%20of%20maybe%20new%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20outcome%2C%20it's%20clear%20that%20AI%20is%20making%20candidates%20nervous%2C%20said%20Padberg.%20Even%20strong%20candidates%20are%20asking%20more%20questions%20about%20what%20AI%20will%20mean%20for%20entry-level%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcKinsey's%20pitch%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20increasingly%20about%20%26quot%3Bcareer%20security%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20job%20security%20%E2%80%94%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20firm's%20training%2C%20network%2C%20and%20problem-solving%20toolkit%20will%20remain%20valuable%2C%20even%20as%20the%20labor%20market%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20McKinsey%20wants%2C%20Padberg%20said%2C%20is%20someone%20who%20can%20do%20what%20AI%20cannot%20easily%20replicate%3A%20ask%20better%20questions%2C%20apply%20judgment%2C%20build%20trust%2C%20be%20curious%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-ai-agents-creating-upskilling-challenge-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadapt%20as%20the%20work%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20has%20also%20brought%20AI%20into%20other%20parts%20of%20recruiting.%20Last%20year%2C%20it%20introduced%20an%20interview%20component%20that%20asks%20candidates%20to%20use%20a%20publicly%20available%20generative-AI%20tool%20to%20work%20through%20hypothetical%20client%20problems%2C%20Padberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcKinsey%20also%20uses%20an%20AI%20simulator%20to%20train%20interviewers%20and%20has%20begun%20piloting%20an%20AI%20interviewer%20as%20a%20first%20screen%20for%20some%20roles%20that%20serve%20the%20firm%2C%20including%20visual%20graphics%20and%20technology%20positions.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPadberg%20said%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20screen%20more%20people%20without%20being%20constrained%20by%20recruiter%20capacity%2C%20while%20giving%20recruiters%20more%20time%20to%20build%20relationships%20with%20candidates.%20But%2C%20she%20added%2C%20hiring%20decisions%20are%20not%20something%20McKisney%20would%20outsource%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20hire%20humans%3B%20you%20join%20a%20human%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Padberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20the%20in-person%20interview%20is%20absolutely%20crucial.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-interview-ai-recruitment-tool-consulting-quantitative-case-study-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779616321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0334f8c9dd4cb81cda98bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-interview-ai-recruitment-tool-consulting-quantitative-case-study-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22McKinsey%20has%20built%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20help%20candidates%20prepare%20for%20their%20interviews%2C%20and%20discourage%20them%20from%20using%20external%20prep%20services.%22%2C%22author