uity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-31T222111.433-1756659080.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bright%2C%20vibrant%2C%20and%20fragrant%2C%20marigolds%20were%20indispensable%20for%20garlands%2C%20temple%20offerings%2C%20and%20door%20hangings%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-31T222111.433-1756659080.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-31T222111.433-1756659080-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-31T222111.433-1756659080-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-31T222111.433-1756659080-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-31T222111.433-1756659080-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-494325%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBright%2C%20vibrant%2C%20and%20fragrant%2C%20marigolds%20were%20indispensable%20for%20garlands%2C%20temple%20offerings%2C%20and%20door%20hangings.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fold-indian-woman-planting-young-tree-2453636497%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20gardens%20were%20living%20spaces%20with%20purpose%2C%20where%20flowers%20brightened%20homes%2C%20aided%20in%20worship%2C%20or%20offered%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading