two%20years%2C%20not%20a%20single%20case%20of%20suicide%20was%20reported.%20Now%2C%20the%20department%20wants%20us%20to%20train%20600%20more%20teachers%20to%20reach%20over%2020%2C000%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ashok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Ashok%20says%2C%20the%20foundation%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20more%20than%2026%2C000%20underprivileged%20children%20across%20the%20country%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Daman%20and%20Diu%2C%20and%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20game%20that%20changes%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Ashok%2C%20OSCAR%20has%20always%20been%20about%20more%20than%20football.%20It%20is%20about%20breaking%20cycles%20of%20poverty%20and%20giving%20children%20the%20mentorship%20they%20never%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2037%2C%20after%20nearly%20two%20decades%2C%20Ashok%20still%20carries%20the%20same%20fire%20he%20had%20at%2018.%20Only%20now%2C%20instead%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20children%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20inspiring%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSports%20are%20not%20a%20luxury.%20They%20are%20as%20necessary%20as%20education.%20Education%20keeps%20a%20child%20in%20school.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334155%2Fbengaluru-ngo-dream-a-dream-educates-underprivileged-children-life-skills-happiness-curriculum-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFootball%20keeps%20a%20child%20alive%20with%20hope%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Together%2C%20they%20change%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%3A%20OSCAR%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757298600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496964%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ashok%20Rathod%20founded%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20keep%20children